{"tid":2190760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成功取決於犠牲的程度","createTime":"2020-09-06T03:19:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T02:59:00.000Z","uid":326037,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"faad8c22414105f538a7a976f9b794ba5878ab28","tid":2190760,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T03:19:32.000Z","msg":"犠牲永不白費 但要其他人知道 令他人改變看法<br />\n<br />\n無決心承擔苦痛 就難享自由民主<br />\n<br />\n偉大的代價就是責任。<br />\n<br />\n一個人絕對不可在遇到危險的威脅時，背過身去試圖逃避。若是這樣做，只會使危險加倍。但是如果立即面對它毫不退縮，危險便會減半。<br />\n<br />\n你們問我們的目標是什麼我可以用一個單詞來回答：勝利，以一切代價去贏得勝利，無論勝利來的多麼恐怖無論道路多麼遙遠和艱辛，沒有勝利就不可能有生存。<br />\n<br />\n在戰爭與屈辱面前，你選擇了屈辱！可是，屈辱過後，你仍得面對戰爭！<br />\n<br />\n決不屈服，決不屈服，決不，決不，決不，決不&mdash;&mdash;除了對於榮譽和智慧的信念，不向任何事物低頭，不管是宏大還是渺小，不管是重要還是瑣碎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z5TF8HM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ5TF8HM.png&h=6a3ff5cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f022378e88d08657e0b741880e0a96d258cda275","tid":2190760,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T04:05:57.000Z","msg":"服從威權<br />\n<br />\n把壞事做盡<br />\n<br />\n才能傾倒大夏<br />\n<br />\n成功解放大陸"},{"pid":"3efedf70b490b6307e83805cfc7182dfd7adb141","tid":2190760,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T04:08:38.000Z","msg":"泛民月薪10萬立法會議員願意犧牲的程度是多少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4975928/org/50ff28d4b0514990e4804f383dbec694.jpg/Yu2uhne2sB2k4eb8pf_MyrFslsq12b07Iu5A0yLuQNM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4975928%2Forg%2F50ff28d4b0514990e4804f383dbec694.jpg%2FYu2uhne2sB2k4eb8pf_MyrFslsq12b07Iu5A0yLuQNM&h=74fef9e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2900e547394d79e3055f8588c88b71161b4ecfda","tid":2190760,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3efedf70b490b6307e83805cfc7182dfd7adb141","tid":2190760,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"